alse,"id":11,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":94356,"username":"fox0001","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fox0001","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/38d5afa82294015541a86339ac95259b?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/38d5afa82294015541a86339ac95259b?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/38d5afa82294015541a86339ac95259b?s=73&d=retro","created":1422439185,"last_modified":1676791090},"last_reply_by":"felixcode","last_touched":1687668391,"title":"[聊聊]红帽限制对 RHEL 源代码的访问，被评价为破坏生态…","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/951378","created":1687662217,"deleted":0,"content":"看到这个文章，我有点不太理解。\r\n\r\n[红帽破坏生态，AlmaLinux 公布未来规划]( https://www.oschina.net/news/246412/almalinux-rhel)\r\n  \r\n### 1. 红帽变了\r\n\r\n- 是的，被 IBM 收购了。\r\n- 我记得红帽有送股份给 Linus ，我曾经觉得红帽很懂感恩。\r\n- 记得第一次认识 CentOS ，我反而是觉得 CentOS 直接从一个商业系统的源码编译出来，好不好？但是这样做完全合法。CentOS 存在这么多年，我甚至觉得红帽很大方。\r\n\r\n### 2. 红帽是商业公司，是为了赚钱而存在，起码其员工需要吃饭。\r\n\r\n- 不排除是被 IBM 高层逼出来的决定。\r\n- 我对此感到遗憾，并且不能认同其做法，但是我能理解其目的。\r\n- 同类的事件，比如 IFTTT 变成收费版（虽然有免费使用额度）。\r\n\r\n### 3. 使用 RHEL 源码编译出来的分发版，对 RHEL 的贡献是多少？\r\n\r\n- 或者说，能不能让 RHEL 赚更多的钱？显然答案是不能。\r\n\r\n### 4. 大家有非用 RHEL 不可的需求吗？\r\n\r\n- 曾经很无知地用过 CentOS 作为私人电脑的系统。后来才明白到，作为桌面用户，Ubuntu 之类的分发版才符合我的需求。再后来就一直用 Lubuntu 了。\r\n- 家里的小服务器、VPS ，我都装了 Debian 。Debian 不是最好的分发版，但我用起来顺手（熟悉、文档多、比较稳定），就够了。","content_rendered":"<p>看到这个文章，我有点不太理解。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.oschina.net/news/246412/almalinux-rhel\" rel=\"nofollow\">红帽破坏生态，AlmaLinux 公布未来规划</a></p>\n<h3>1. 红帽变了</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>是的，被 IBM 收购了。</li>\n<li>我记得红帽有送股份给 Linus ，我曾经觉得红帽很懂感恩。</li>\n<li>记得第一次认识 CentOS ，我反而是觉得 CentOS 直接从一个商业系统的源码编译出来，好不好？但是这样做完全合法。CentOS 存在这么多年，我甚至觉得红帽很大方。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>2. 红帽是商业公司，是为了赚钱而存在，起码其员工需要吃饭。</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>不排除是被 IBM 高层逼出来的决定。</li>\n<li>我对此感到遗憾，并且不能认同其做法，但是我能理解其目的。</li>\n<li>同类的事件，比如 IFTTT 变成收费版（虽然有免费使用额度）。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>3. 使用 RHEL 源码编译出来的分发版，对 RHEL 的贡献是多少？</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>或者说，能不能让 RHEL 赚更多的钱？显然答案是不能。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>4. 大家有非用 RHEL 不可的需求吗？</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>曾经很无知地用过 CentOS 作为私人电脑的系统。后来才明白到，作为桌面用户，Ubuntu 之类的分发版才符合我的需求。再后来就一直用 Lubuntu 了。</li>\n<li>家里的小服务器、VPS ，我都装了 Debian 。Debian 不是最好的分发版，但我用起来顺手（熟悉、文档多、比较稳定），就够了。</li>\n</ul>\n","last_modified":1687662816,"replies":32,"id":951378},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":56813,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","stars":8441,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":595319,"username":"MFWT","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/MFWT","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e8fd/8801/595319_mini.png?m=1686658599","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e8fd/8801/595319_normal.png?m=1686658599","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e8fd/8801/595319_large.png?m=1686658599","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e8fd/8801/595319_xlarge.png?m=1686658599","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e8fd/8801/595319_xlarge.png?m=1686658599","created":1664105935,"last_modified":1686658599},"last_reply_by":"id80108900","last_touched":1687668818,"title":"这下真的玩出屁来了，读大专去了","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/951401","created":1687664697,"deleted":0,"content":"### 物理类本科线 439\r\n\r\n### 老子：\r\n[![VIGY4P.md.jpeg]( https://i.imgloc.com/2023/06/25/VIGY4P.md.jpeg)]( https://imgloc.com/i/VIGY4P)","content_rendered":"<h3>物理类本科线 439</h3>\n<h3>老子：</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgloc.com/i/VIGY4P\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"VIGY4P.md.jpeg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgloc.com/2023/06/25/VIGY4P.md.jpeg\"/></a></p>\n","last_modified":1687664697,"replies":29,"id":951401},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_large.png?m=1650127482","name":"shanghai","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_normal.png?m=1650127482","title":"上海","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/shanghai","topics":3235,"footer":"","header":"","title_alternative":"Shanghai","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_mini.png?m=1650127482","stars":2209,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":18,"parent_node_name":"cn"},"member":{"id":45946,"username":"Henrybsbhp","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Henrybsbhp","website":"","twitter":"Henrybsbhp","psn":"Henrybsbhp","github":"","btc":"","location":"An Qing","tagline":"Nothing is true, everything is permitted","bio":"「 」","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0115/afca/45946_mini.png?m=1653586126","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0115/afca/45946_normal.png?m=1653586126","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0115/afca/45946_large.png?m=1653586126","created":1380093861,"last_modified":1653586126},"last_reply_by":"windpinw","last_touched":1687662689,"title":"「求助」座標上海，最近想買車上綠牌，苦於沒有居住證。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/951348","created":1687658973,"deleted":0,"content":"先交待下背景：\r\n\r\n1. 安徽戶口；\r\n2. 來滬兩年半，社保已繳滿 24 個月以上；\r\n3. 現住商住房，酒店式公寓那種。無法備案，故無法辦理居住證；\r\n4. 沒有交通違規紀錄；\r\n5. 本人不喜歡汽車，不喜引擎聲，不會考慮油車。\r\n\r\n最近我想買輛特斯拉 Model Y ，每天上班來回 30 公里通勤和回老家時用。現在是騎自行車在上班，但苦於下雨天騎車 30 公里來回實在不方便。遂想買一輛 Model Y ，回老家也比較方便。\r\n\r\n昨天找到特斯拉銷售問了下，說上滬牌必須要有居住證。我因沒有且無法辦理居住證，銷售就提供了以下幾個方案給我：\r\n\r\n1. 找黄牛辦居住證，費用在第一年 2300 左右，但要半年以後才能到手。這樣肯定錯過今年的上牌政策，明年形勢也不明朗；\r\n2. 找有上海居住證的親戚、朋友把綠牌掛靠在他們名下；\r\n3. 自己開個皮包公司，然後以公司的名義購車上滬牌。這樣每年需要找人給公司代理記帳；\r\n4. 上外地牌照，但高峰期內環和高架限行。\r\n\r\n我沒買過車，不太懂這些方案中哪個比較可行，想請教下有經驗的人士來幫我出出對策，感謝。\r\n\r\n\r\nPS. 打繁體字是因爲我用倉頡，打簡體不太方便，並且本人非港澳臺人士。大家勿糾結這點，謝謝。","content_rendered":"<p>先交待下背景：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>安徽戶口；</li>\n<li>來滬兩年半，社保已繳滿 24 個月以上；</li>\n<li>現住商住房，酒店式公寓那種。無法備案，故無法辦理居住證；</li>\n<li>沒有交通違規紀錄；</li>\n<li>本人不喜歡汽車，不喜引擎聲，不會考慮油車。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>最近我想買輛特斯拉 Model Y ，每天上班來回 30 公里通勤和回老家時用。現在是騎自行車在上班，但苦於下雨天騎車 30 公里來回實在不方便。遂想買一輛 Model Y ，回老家也比較方便。</p>\n<p>昨天找到特斯拉銷售問了下，說上滬牌必須要有居住證。我因沒有且無法辦理居住證，銷售就提供了以下幾個方案給我：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>找黄牛辦居住證，費用在第一年 2300 左右，但要半年以後才能到手。這樣肯定錯過今年的上牌政策，明年形勢也不明朗；</li>\n<li>找有上海居住證的親戚、朋友把綠牌掛靠在他們名下；</li>\n<li>自己開個皮包公司，然後以公司的名義購車上滬牌。這樣每年需要找人給公司代理記帳；</li>\n<li>上外地牌照，但高峰期內環和高架限行。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>我沒買過車，不太懂這些方案中哪個比較可行，想請教下有經驗的人士來幫我出出對策，感謝。</p>\n<p>PS. 打繁體字是因爲我用倉頡，打簡體不太方便，並且本人非港澳臺人士。大家勿糾結這點，謝謝。</p>\n","last_modified":1687658973,"replies":28,"id":951348},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":56813,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","stars":8441,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":397242,"username":"pipinstallpy","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/pipinstallpy","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d81d/edeb/397242_mini.png?m=1684994643","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d81d/edeb/397242_normal.png?m=1684994643","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d81d/edeb/397242_large.png?m=1684994643","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d81d/edeb/397242_xlarge.png?m=1684994643","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d81d/edeb/397242_xlarge.png?m=1684994643","created":1554082898,"last_modified":1684994643},"last_reply_by":"pipinstallpy","last_touched":1687666902,"title":"中国企业在非法解聘中，行政是最大的帮凶","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/951385","created":1687663545,"d